1
00:00:00,600 --> 00:00:04,800
Wardha district, Maharashtra — 15 public health centres, 1,600 patients a day.

2
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:08,800
Every dot is a live facility health score. Two are in crisis.

3
00:00:09,500 --> 00:00:14,300
Click a facility. HealthGrid doesn't just show data — it explains it.

4
00:00:14,600 --> 00:00:20,000
Stock-outs in 2 days. Half the doctors absent. Patients up 36%.

5
00:00:20,800 --> 00:00:24,400
The AI recommends a guarded stock transfer. One click to approve.

6
00:00:24,600 --> 00:00:28,100
Executed as a live transaction — both facilities re-score instantly.

7
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:33,400
Ask the Health Copilot anything — English, हिंदी or मराठी.

8
00:00:33,700 --> 00:00:42,000
It answers only from live district data — grounded, cited, actionable.

9
00:00:43,000 --> 00:00:47,300
Now the frontline. A health worker picks their language…

10
00:00:47,800 --> 00:00:53,800
…and simply speaks: "आज ओआरएस का स्टॉक 50 बचा है"

11
00:00:54,300 --> 00:01:01,500
Gemini turns speech into a structured update — confirmed by the worker, never auto-applied.

12
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:07,800
No forms. No paperwork. No English required.

13
00:01:08,600 --> 00:01:12,300
And the district command center reacts in seconds.

14
00:01:12,500 --> 00:01:15,900
30-day projection: all 54 stock-out days prevented, zero new stock. HealthGrid AI.
